'''David Standridge''' is an American politician from the state of [[Alabama]]. A member of the [[Republican Party (United States)|Republican Party]], Standridge serves in the [[Alabama House of Representatives]], representing the 34th district.

Standridge was elected to the Alabama House in 2012. He previously served as a [[probate judge]] in [[Blount County, Alabama]].<ref>http://blog.al.com/spotnews/2012/12/republican_officials_welcome_s.html</ref>

